Package mindustry.net

Class Administration.Config

java.lang.Object
mindustry.net.Administration.Config
Enclosing class:
Administration
public static class Administration.Config extends Object
Server configuration definition. Each config value can be a string, boolean or number. Creating a new Config instance implicitly adds it to the list of server configs. This can be used for custom plugin configuration.
